The '''Thailand Institute of Nuclear Technology (TINT)''' ('''Thai name:''' สถาบันเทคโนโลยีนิวเคลียร์แห่งชาติ) is a public organization in [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]].<ref>http://www.most.go.th/main/en/375-ministry-of-science-and-technology/agencies-under-most/4516-thailand-institute-of-nuclear-technology-public-orga</ref> [[File:TRR1-M1-Reactor.jpg|thumb|TRR1/M1 research reactor at the Thailand Institute of Nuclear Technology]]
